I had problem with soar throat and it was infected. So I could not swallow or drink or eat anything. She understood my problem so well and gave the appropriate medicine.

Fortunately I found the doctor and was treated and healed in a days time. The nurse who gave me injection did incredible work. I never felt the pain at all. Not even after returning home. 

I will definitely recommend the doctor. Thank you so much.

I visited the doctor due to severe headache and I have been suffering from headaches for almost 2 months Doctor was patient enough,Listens carefully and probes well to understand the root cause and confirmed it was a migraine and the best part is that, she gives a lot of advice on lifestyle changes to overcome the issue instead of prescribing unnecessary medications. She did prescribe few medicines but very few and cost-effective ones. Best doctor and the other 2 staffs in the hospital were welcoming and too good, they did follow up the next day to check if I am doing good. Highly recommended.

The doctor was very polite and patiently listened to all the problems that I explained. The staff was very cooperative. Overall excellent review. I would definitely recommend others to visit the clinic, and I would for sure visit it again in the future.

The doctor is very polite , explains the problem in detail, guides the patient about the medicines and precautions to be taken. The staff is very caring. Consultation fee and medicines prescribed are very reasonable.
